ai-patthana14.28:0.2_0: (The teachings should be expanded as in the previous discourse.)
ai-patthana14.28:0.3_0: And she try to throw it out into the process.
ai-patthana14.28:1.1_0: Without seeing things that should be given up, they don’t give up causes and conditions for the reason.
ai-patthana14.28:1.1_1: Not seeing should be given up by seeing. Cruence should be given up by seeing.
ai-patthana14.28:2.1_0: There are nine based on the six elements ...
